  <dashboards>
    <dashboard name='Findings and Recommendation' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>Portfolio Findings and Recommendation</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='794' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1016' minheight='964' minwidth='1016' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='7' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
            <zone h='5083' id='8' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='93257' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='5913'>
              <zone fixed-size='278' h='28838' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='5913' />
              <zone h='64419' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='34751'>
                <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                  <story-points>
                    <story-point caption='1. Target High-Burden Regions with Protective Structures&#10;Sub-Saharan Africa, Middle East, and South Asia show extreme poverty rates exceeding 100% and child mortality of 115,438 in low-income countries—yet these same regions experienced inflation spikes peaking at 10K during 2020-2023. Prioritize healthcare and infrastructure investments here, but mandate inflation-linked hedging and local currency protections to manage volatility.&#10;2.Capitalize on GDP-Poverty Disconnects for Inclusive Growth Alpha&#10;The scatter plot reveals outliers where GDP per capita reaches $1,200 while poverty rates stay near 50K, signaling severe inequality amid growth. Shift portfolio weighting from pure GDP plays to financial inclusion, SME lending, and education technology in these markets to capture alpha from structural inefficiencies while driving poverty reduction.' captured-sheet='Global Poverty Analysis' id='1' />
                  </story-points>
                </flipboard>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{673631DF-B710-470D-BA9A-03D2496D10A8}' />
    </dashboard>
